---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
import Cta from "@components/cta.astro";

export const prerender = true;
export const lastModified = '2025-03-25';
---

<Layout title="Ansible & Python Training">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Ansible & Python Training</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Master Automation, Configuration Management, and Machine Learning Workflows</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">
      Enhance your IT skills with Luca Berton’s Ansible & Python Training. Learn automation, configuration management, and machine learning integration to drive efficiency and innovation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mt-6">Why Learn Ansible & Python?</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2">
      Ansible is a leading automation tool, simplifying IT tasks such as configuration management, application deployment, and system administration. Python complements Ansible by offering advanced scripting capabilities, API integrations, and machine learning workflows. Together, they create a powerful automation ecosystem that enhances IT infrastructure management.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mt-6">Training Highlights</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-500 mt-2">
      <li>Hands-on Ansible Playbook Development for Infrastructure Automation.</li>
      <li>Understanding Ansible Architecture and Best Practices.</li>
      <li>Advanced Python Scripting for automation and data processing.</li>
      <li>Building Custom Ansible Modules with Python.</li>
      <li>Machine Learning Workflow Automation using Python.</li>
      <li>Scaling automation across multi-cloud and hybrid environments.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">
      Whether you’re an IT professional, DevOps engineer, or cloud architect, mastering Ansible & Python will streamline your operations, reduce manual effort, and enhance your organization's digital transformation.
    </p>
  </Container>
  <Cta />
</Layout>
